{"operationName":"customer","variables":{},"query":"query customer($parameters: CustomerQueryParameters) {
  customer(parameters: $parameters) {
    firstName
    lastName
    city
    email
    bonusRubles
    availableBonusRubles
    personalOffersCount
    favoriteShopId
    type
    userId
    cityId
    __typename
  }
}
"}
